    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4947364>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Type locality of Apistogramma ortegai. Peru, Departamento Loreto, Distrito Pebas, small stream tributary of Ampiyacu River." ;
